If you put a Chaos unit in a team with another realm, that team is considered Pure for the purpose of calculating the effects of Realm Mastery and the Realm Mechanics (as if you only used units from that realm), with additional bonuses:
Universal: Every realm that is mixed with chaos automatically get +100% Death Resist At the start of the exploration;
* In Aequor: Increases tentacle base damage by 1% of Max HP for every Chaos in team; Chaos exalt also increases Tentacle Assembly (number of tentacles attacks for the turn) by 1 (Normally you will get 1 tentacle after Exalt, while exalting in Chaos Aequor gives you 2) and charges 10 Aliemus for all Aequor teammates;
* In Caro: Chaos units exalting increases Embryo Fusion by 25%;
* In Ultra: Permanently reduce enemy attack by 0,5% Max hp, increase all allies Strength by 1% Max HP, increase all Ultra unit's CRate and CDMG by 10% for every Chaos in team.
